snippet: Matt Kenseth won the Nascar Sprint Cup series race at Talladega after a large last-lap crash turned the defending series champion, Tony Stewart, upside down.
abstract: Matt Kenseth wins Nascar Sprint Cup series race at Talladega Raceway.
